Package arcade.patch.agent.process

Class PatchProcessInflammation

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.patch.agent.process.PatchProcess
      • arcade.patch.agent.process.PatchProcessInflammation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Process
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PatchProcessInflammationCD8
    public abstract class PatchProcessInflammation
extends PatchProcess
    Implementation of Process for inflammation type modules in which IL-2 is taken up and cytotoxic/stimulatory functions are modified.

    The Inflammation module represents an 8-component signaling network.

    • Constructor Detail

      • PatchProcessInflammation

        public PatchProcessInflammation​(PatchCellCART cell)
        Creates an Inflammation module for the given PatchCellCART.

        Module parameters are specific for the cell population. The module starts with no IL-2 bound and no three-chain receptors. Daughter cells split amounts of bound IL-2 and three-chain receptors upon dividing.

        Parameters:
        cell - the PatchCellCART the module is associated with
